There are many ways of sending HTML templates:

first:
      Write your own HTML code & run it to browser and press ctl+A and ctrl+C
second:
      Open your email and write your subject & below in message section ctrl+V
third:
      send
===============================================================================



first:
      Write your own HTML code press ctl+A & ctrl+C
second:
      Open your email and write your subject & below in message section write [anything] & press ctrl+shift+C or Right Click & Inspect Element
      and hover on what ever wrote on message section [anything].
      and paste your code.
      
third:
      send
